f4dba6bab8fb558c2e49694d6b712","tid":136241,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得閒搵下班美國同事八下先<br />\n都幾多係黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點睇浸浸"},{"pid":"eca9d3875eac756dd37981718c5ac0feeae4d322","tid":136241,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a66212d8a2330df6522e15328957c04be9402a","tid":136241,"uid":40588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇美國巴打講下美國係咪咁慘<br />\n<br />\n我就咁睇篇文覺得美國好似就係滅國邊緣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上海讀書既人寫的 唔知係鬼佬定地道支那"},{"pid":"d337c7f38b98ed83573123276897c281f17fa201","tid":136241,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2996e5c325c4fb6f28fd7de3e08e21f019f0b5b8","tid":136241,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb41c1541571be5dc022bfc2f74917f7bb581d8","tid":136241,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beecde6551e2fa68b443bb5012ecf592433f1262","tid":136241,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇美國巴打講下美國係咪咁慘<br />\n<br />\n我就咁睇篇文覺得美國好似就係滅國邊緣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住開一個安寧既社區，自從有堆某地既有證加無證移民後，開始三日唔埋就有一戶俾人爆格<br />\n唔撚知關唔關事喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm